#!/bin/bash
# Factorial Logic
read -p "Enter a number for factorial: " num
fact=1
for (( i=1; i<=num; i++ )); do
    fact=$((fact * i))
done
echo "Factorial of $num is: $fact"

# Delete lines with specific word
read -p "Enter filename to edit: " filename
read -p "Enter word to remove lines: " word
sed -i "/$word/d" "$filename"
echo "Lines containing '$word' have been removed from $filename."
